## Follow Users [/api/users/{userid}/follow]

### Follow a user [POST]

You can follow a user.

+ Parameters
    + userid (number) - ID of the target User in the form of an integer
    
+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.XbPfbIHMI6arZ3Y922BhjWgQzWXcXNrz0ogtVhfEd2o
    
    + Body

            {
                "user_id": 1,
                "follower_id": 2
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "message": "You are now following that user." 
            }
            
## Like Posts [/api/posts/{postid}/like]

### Like a User Post [POST]

Like a post by a user.

+ Parameters
    + postid (number) - ID of the Post in the form of an integer

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.XbPfbIHMI6arZ3Y922BhjWgQzWXcXNrz0ogtVhfEd2o
    
    + Body

            {
                "user_id": 1,
                "post_id": 243
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "message": "Post liked!" 
            }